data.enText: a Christian religious song sung at Christmas
to sing sth in a cheerful way

tr: a joyful song (usually celebrating the birth of Christ)
joyful religious song celebrating the birth of Christ

example: They went caroling on Christmas Day

value.def: Carols are Christian religious songs that are sung at Christmas.

example.ex: The singing of Christmas carols is a custom derived from early dance routines of pagan origin...
example.tran: 唱圣诞颂歌的风俗源自异教徒早期的舞蹈仪式。
在门口唱圣诞颂歌的人

trans: 圣诞报佳音(常指在教堂或户外唱圣诞颂歌)
